 <span data-ttu-id="dfa13-321">이제 ElementsWithOnlyAttributes.xml를 만듭니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dfa13-321">Now create ElementsWithOnlyAttributes.xml:</span></span>  
  
